quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  53,33,"Phir aey Nabi, tumne us shaks ko bhi dekha jo raah-e-khuda se phir gaya"
  53,34,Aur thoda sa de kar ruk gaya
  53,35,Kya uske paas gaib ka ilm hai ke woh haqeeqat ko dekh raha hai
  53,36,Kya usey un baaton ki koi khabar nahin pahunchi jo moosa ke sahifon
  53,37,Aur us Ibrahim ke sahifon mein bayan hui hai jisne wafa ka haqq ada kar diya
  53,38,Yeh ke koi bojh uthane wala dusre ka bojh nahin uthayega
  53,39,Aur yeh ke Insaan ke liye kuch nahin hai magar woh jiski usne saii(koshish /Strive) ki hai
  53,40,Aur yeh ke uski saii (koshih/strive/effort) anqareeb dekhi jayegi
  53,41,Aur uski puri jaza use di jayegi
  53,42,Aur yeh ke aakhir-e-kaar pahunchna tere Rubb hi ke paas hai
  53,43,Aur yeh ke usi ne hasaya aur usi ne rulaya
  53,44,Aur yeh ke usi ne maut di aur usi ne zindagi bakshi
  53,45,Aur yeh ke usi ne narr (male) aur maada (female) ka joda paida kiya
  53,46,Ek boond (sperm-drop) se jab woh tapkayi jati hai
  53,47,Aur yeh ke dusri zindagi bakshna bhi usi ke zimme hai
  53,48,Aur yeh ke usi ne gani (enriches) kiya aur jaidad bakshi
  53,49,Aur yeh ke wahi sheraa (Sirius / mighty star) ka Rubb hai
  53,50,Aur yeh ke usi ne Aad-e-oola (people of Aad) ko halaak kiya
  53,51,Aur samood ko aisa mitaya ke unmein se kisi ko baaki na choda
  53,52,Aur unse pehle qaum-e-Nooh ko tabaah kiya kyunke woh thay hi sakht zaalim-o-sarkash log
  53,53,Aur aundhi girne wali bastiyon ko utha phenka. (Qaum-e-Lut)
  53,54,Phir chaa diya unpar woh kuch jo (tum jaante hi ho ke) kya chaa diya
  53,55,"Pas aey mukhatib, apne Rubb ki kin kin niyamaton mein tu shakk karega"
  53,56,Yeh ek tambeeh (warning) hai pehle aaye huye tambihaat(warnings) mein se
  53,57,Aane wali ghadi qareeb aa lagi hai
  53,58,Allah ke siwa koi usko hatane wala nahin
  53,59,Ab kya yahi woh baatein hain jinpar tum izhaar- e-taajub karte ho
  53,60,Hanste(laugh) ho aur rotey (weep) nahin ho
  53,61,Aur gaa (singing) bajaa kar inhein taalte ho
  53,62,Jhuk jao Allah ke aagey aur bandagi baja laaoo (ayat-e-sajda)